name: Help Three Sexy Beards release #THISGAMEISSWAG (Canceled)
blurb: This is a crazy visual novel from the heads of crazy people. If you have mental problems then you will enjoy it by all means.

rewards.reward: We will mention you in a special thanks section with each game.

An e-mail personalized for you. It may include a picture or haiku or video. Either way it will be unique. People who pledged $10 or more to get gifts at higher levels will not have this gift unless stated otherwise.

Everything related to the game will be sent to you before the release. It will most likely be around March, but with us who knows? You will get it before the con date though by at least two weeks. You also get our love and thanks. As an added bonus you will get Tyler's doodles from his History class.
You will be getting a copy of the game and a special cassette tape of songs from me. Both will be redeemable through the con or mail.
You get everything listed so far (including the e-mail). You will also get a free copy of the game redeemable at the con or through the mail. We will contact you on the details.

You have just pre-ordered the game for you and someone else. That lucky person. You will also receive a mix CD of our favorite songs. We will get in contact with you on how you will receive both games. You may pick it up at the con or get it through the mail.

You have pre-ordered three copies of the game as well as the soundtrack. The soundtrack is meant only for you, but you could always send it to other people. Not like we care. If you are at the con we will also scream how much we love you in public. We will then hug you. If you cannot make the con then we will think of something else to equal this reward of some fashion on the internet. As with the others we will contact you for mailing address or some way to pick up at the con.

You get reward below (including the e-mail) with five copies of the game. We seriously just want to make lots of copies of this game. We will also send you a special mix CD that has some of our favorite songs.

You get reward number 8. You will also get the added bonus of reward 6. In addition you will receive a "song" that I will write just for you about how much I love you. You may also sit with us at the con if you go.
Reward 9 with the added bonus of getting to sit with us at any con we attend.
We will actually let YOU make a reward. It has to be within our limits. But as long as we can do it, you can choose it. Unless it is a reward coming up.
I will send messages of your choice to any voice actor or musician you want for a week. I recommend you choose someone you hate and mean messages. I do those well. You also get rewards 8 and below.

The ultimate reward. You get every reward thus far including 9. You will be our best friend. We will spam you everywhere we possibly can as the coolest person. I will change me gamertag and steam name to your name. Tyler will do something similar. We will add you on everything we can. You will also receive a special place on our last.fm walls. Love you, person who chose this reward. Also worth noting is that Tyler is offering his own records and CDs for this reward. He will even make you a ten minute lolicore song.
